Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:34.99,sign_2158_1_From_One_Year_to,Title,0000,0000,0000,,From One Year to the Next
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:37.66,sign_2278_2_Coffee_Shop,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be Christmas soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:41.53,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:44.80,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to do some kind of event.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:47.16,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Something to bring in more customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:48.79,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:52.29,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we put on another play \Non Christmas Eve, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:57.17,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It would be the Hitotose Troupe's \Nsecond performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:57.96,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:01.87,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have much time until Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:06.45,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,so we probably won't be able \Nto do one as big as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:07.94,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,We won't have time to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:10.11,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,A short play is fine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:11.29,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.17,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Principal Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:14.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.95,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I bet our second play will go \Neven better than the first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.86,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it! It'll be about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:23.11,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:24.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For the end of the year...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.70,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe {\i1}Chushingura{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:28.67,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Since it'll be Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:31.57,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe it should be more of a Christmas story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:34.44,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas story, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:36.59,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:41.33,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,A tragic love story between \NSanta Claus and a reindeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wherefore are thou a reindeer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:44.82,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.72,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:51.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,A revenge drama about Prince Santa Claus \Ndriven mad with the need for vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:52.85,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the convent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:55.97,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:58.85,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what do those have \Nto do with Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:00.74,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,other than having Santa and a reindeer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.53,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I like it! Santa and his reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.62,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to start preparing \Nthe costumes right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:10.16,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan's switch just flipped on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.75,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait until the costume fitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:16.61,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know! You'll need dresses, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.65,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Mayu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.39,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:24.23,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said before, we won't have much time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:27.26,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,so I was thinking of borrowing \Ncostumes from the theater club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:31.22,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,D'oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:31.78,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan's switch just flipped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:32.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:36.77,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, how about something \Nbased on {\i1}A Christmas Carol{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.10,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That might be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:43.41,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,On Christmas Eve night, a cruel, \Nmiserly girl is haunted by a ghost,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:47.49,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,who asks Santa Claus and \Nhis reindeer for a certain gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:50.49,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You won't budge on Santa \Nand the reindeer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:51.16,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:54.69,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, but if it has that many characters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.67,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,won't we be short on actors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:02.50,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,We have the landlady, Hina-chan, \Nand Yua-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.96,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:09.43,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,If we can get a real reindeer, \Nwe should be able to manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:13.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,If a regular deer will work instead of \Na reindeer, I might be able to get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:16.05,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,W-We can do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:19.03,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Animals do like Hina-chan, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:21.82,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could summon \NSanta while you're at it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:26.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Um, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.56,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you think my grandpa \Nwould be good enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:33.05,Main Dialogue Top,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't know if I can act...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.05,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you don't need to \Nworry about it that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.71,sign_6563_69_Used_Bookstore__,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Used Bookstore\N Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.71,sign_6566_70___The_Next_Day__,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(652,1)}~ The Next Day ~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.96,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing a play on Christmas Eve, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:44.97,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Let me help... you... with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:46.47,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.45,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.22,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:50.72,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I went straight to the theater club \Nto borrow costumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.28,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:00.71,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,And I also came up with a practice schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.73,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.24,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:04.40,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Kuina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.74,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,And Mayuki-senpai, here's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.11,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chiaki-senpai! \NPlease try on your costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:13.36,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll fit, but it's a little different\N from normal costumes, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:23.63,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a spirit costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.45,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:31.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-It fit perfectly when I tried it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:35.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you call an \N"unequal bodily society"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:38.15,sign_8048_93_Fujimiya__Girls_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Fujimiya \NGirls' \NHigh \NSchool
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:41.27,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be holding a play on the 24th!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.31,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Please take one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:43.28,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.14,Main Dialogue Top,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.78,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Please take one! And be sure to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.15,Main Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.23,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be really fun, so please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.41,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.38,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:58.17,sign_8486_103_The_Hitotose_Tro,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Hitotose Troupe \NDecember 24 \N{\c&HBF3EC8&}Mini {\c&H4041D2&}Drama
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:58.17,sign_8486_104_Place__Coffee_Sh,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Place: Coffee Shop Hitotose \NStarting at 5:00 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:58.17,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,December 24th... A mini-drama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.53,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting on another play \Nat Hitotose Manor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:03.13,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We hope you'll come watch it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.88,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.64,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of play is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.30,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's based on {\i1}A Christmas Carol{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.18,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,That's certainly a classic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.17,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a real deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.04,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,And Chiaki-senpai will strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:17.46,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.52,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.06,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.81,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.78,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You really did call a deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:32.32,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.52,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,take the deer with you \Nto draw in customers, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:44.09,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,W-We'll be holding a play \Nhere in our shop today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:49.09,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please come and... w-watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:53.39,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why did I have to dress like this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:01.25,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, I can't do this! \NIt's too embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:05.52,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan's a scarecrow already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.11,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.56,Main Dialogue,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,A deer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.74,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.62,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.12,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:25.62,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, Mayu-chan, how goes the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:30.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The deer's doing all the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.13,sign_10799_134_Performance__in_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Performance\N in Session
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:37.64,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sensei, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:39.63,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like business is booming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:42.52,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a full house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:42.52,Main Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Please grant my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.71,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Your play is getting a good response.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:47.40,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot grant the wish of a miser like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:47.40,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not so much the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:51.40,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I beseech thee, grant her wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.40,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's the landlady's costume
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.11,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,and the deer that are popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:59.08,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. So you actually have \Na real deer in the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.37,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:04.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I'll try to win people over \Nwith the actual story!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:09.17,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,A deer... a deer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.93,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll try to use that \Nin my next drama script.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:13.91,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.68,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:24.11,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, since this was \Nyour second performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:27.23,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,your acting felt much more \Nnatural than in the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.69,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,It was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.18,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:32.80,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's to be expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:36.41,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Being praised by Sensei \Nreally gives me an appetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It should give you inspiration, \Nnot an appetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.41,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.58,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll have to take my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're leaving already, Ruri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:51.39,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There's still lots of cake \Nand other things left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.59,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I've had plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:59.72,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You need to go home and get to bed, \Nor Santa won't come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to bed early today, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.66,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, do you actually \Nstill believe in Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.33,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako-san is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.57,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go home and get to bed early,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.99,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,or Santa Claus won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.23,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Ruri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.62,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to hang your stocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:26.50,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.28,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei is so mature...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:30.25,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:35.01,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan, I'll go buy presents later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:39.34,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We don't want to \Ncrush Hina-chan's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.66,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.22,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.33,Main Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.84,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.15,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.42,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.29,Main Dialogue,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Your face looks different, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:15.24,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,You usually get all nervous and stiffen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.45,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing theater in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't get nervous as easily anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:26.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can talk \Nthis normally to people now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:33.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone call me a scarecrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:37.32,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan! Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:45.20,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that! It's the \Nfirst sunrise of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan, you're so energetic \Nthis early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:51.94,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the start of a new year \Nbrings all kinds of firsts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.96,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help being excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.07,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,F-Firsts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:56.96,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.32,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The first snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.84,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.11,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The first mochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.47,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The first bite snitched!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.47,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Tangy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.27,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And the first book!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:09.98,sign_15962_207_Discourse_on__De,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1)}Discourse on \NDecadence
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,All you're doing is eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:14.86,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.98,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:21.38,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, you were in my \Nfirst dream of the year, Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.61,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? What was it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:27.54,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,A giant Mayu-chan looking down on Mt. Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.50,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.69,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was that big?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:34.50,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.13,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,But Mt. Fuji was actually a miniature,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:44.26,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,and you were actually even smaller \Nthan you are in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:44.26,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:45.54,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:49.64,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:57.12,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you all have any goals \Nfor the coming year?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:58.02,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:01.41,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is to read 300 books this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.78,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to work on my acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:11.54,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I guess mine is still to be able to talk \Nin front of people without getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:15.97,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,And mine is to keep supporting Hina-chan \Nand the others as their senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:19.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get the coffee shop's \Nbusiness on the right track, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.46,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's drinking so much milk...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:27.30,Italics Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I guess what she really \Nwants to do is get taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.31,Signs,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\pos(534.326,12.05)\fs18\3c&H4C524A&}Please continue \Nto support \NCoffee Shop Hitotose \Nthis year!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:33.31,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kuu-chan, Mayu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.54,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.44,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to visit our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.19,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:39.97,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.07,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back in about two days, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:47.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Two days? Won't you just spend \Nall that time on trains and buses?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:51.33,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Our families live in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.65,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,They're only about an hour away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.46,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.13,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wondered this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:02.05,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the countryside does \NHina-chan live, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.84,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:11.35,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going now, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.33,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be so lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.03,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:19.63,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't goodbye forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.20,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.61,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:30.46,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you get lonely, \Njust imagine this doll is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:35.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll send this little one \Nwith you in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:38.25,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take something that's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:40.44,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll give you this book!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:42.63,Main Dialogue,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not take something half-eaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:54.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Landlady, I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:55.52,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:06.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's so quiet with \Nboth of them gone, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.32,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.94,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:14.16,Italics Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The conversation isn't going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:18.07,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I have to think of something \Nshe'd enjoy talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:21.57,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,If there's one thing I know \Nshe likes, it's theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:25.89,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know that much about theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:29.77,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What else does she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:35.85,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know anything \Nabout her at all, do I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.54,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,everything about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:52.19,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.87,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff about acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:58.79,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:05.50,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,When she puts it that way, \Nthere are too many things I'd like to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:10.26,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Like how she moves her body so gracefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:14.26,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,or how she prepares physically \Nfor each of her roles...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:18.52,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:21.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know about your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:24.60,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:35.56,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so what do you like, other than theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:37.58,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Other than theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.78,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:42.83,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I do like small animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Small animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:49.09,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. When I was little, \NI had a golden hamster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:52.84,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It was so small, and its eyes were so round,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:55.47,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,and its golden fur was so soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:57.97,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It was so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:01.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Golden hamsters \Nreally are cute, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:02.48,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:08.66,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Small, round eyes, golden...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:12.49,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like something \NI've seen before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:17.22,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Mayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.87,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:22.77,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I'm leaving for my \Npart-time job this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.54,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:28.33,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Part-time? You have a part-time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:28.88,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.59,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Every year on New Year's,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.69,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I go and help a friend of mine \Nwho likes theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.72,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And what kind of work is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:42.77,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, serving customers, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.58,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Serving customers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:48.77,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a chance to overcome my nervousness\N right from the start of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.14,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:51.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.98,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This is not what I had envisioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:07.04,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The landlady really does look good \Nin anything she wears, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:10.92,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,All the men here can't take \Ntheir eyes off of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.88,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's someone suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:19.55,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But that hairstyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.06,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:27.06,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:30.78,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm working here with the landlady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.57,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:36.61,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,She gets to see Chiaki-senpai \Nin her miko outfit up close...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.58,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:42.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you come to see the landlady?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:44.58,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Got a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:48.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you go talk to her \Ninstead of sneaking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fan's job to watch over her \Nfrom the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:53.09,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.47,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:57.76,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Ch-Chiaki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was looking at you\N in your miko outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:01.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:05.20,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try being a miko with us, Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:07.23,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.54,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.11,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:15.06,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I get to see Chiaki-senpai \Nin her miko outfit up close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:16.04,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:19.95,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we don't \Nneed to ask the priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.05,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:26.62,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Having two cute mikos \Nshould bring in more visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.42,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put unnecessary pressure on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:38.00,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat lots of mochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.26,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.93,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I ate lots, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:43.79,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The landlady talks \Na lot more than I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:43.80,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, four? That is a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:45.77,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:48.55,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,She's really outgoing with young kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:50.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:51.77,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:56.87,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she does talk a lot \Nwith Mayu-chan and Kuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.23,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.95,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I were smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:06.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Are you picking a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:13.65,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping me today, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:14.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:17.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Miss Landlady...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:23.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,...like to talk with you more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Would that bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:35.72,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't bother me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:38.60,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy you feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.45,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:41.70,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.45,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.89,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:05.97,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I got to know the landlady \Nbetter today, even if it was just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:13.48,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling I'll be able to \Ntalk with her even more tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:19.23,Signs,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:25.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan's doll is all wet with my drool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:32.80,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness, Goro. You really \Nlove Mayu, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:33.62,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:39.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's is almost over...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:41.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It went by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:47.39,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,In three months, \NI'll have been here for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.52,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure how it would go at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.71,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,but then I met everyone, \Nstarted our theater troupe,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:56.02,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,became friends with Yua-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.90,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the play\N at our culture festival, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:02.78,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and the Hitotose Troupe \Nhad its first performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.78,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So much has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:09.78,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's all helped me \Ngrow up a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.08,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:17.92,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.22,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep trying my best at everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:22.05,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:24.76,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:25.80,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:27.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan! Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.55,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.70,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I bought lots of souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.67,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tokyo's specialty, Ahiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:36.31,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I got Ahiru, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:37.94,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So we have lots!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:39.89,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all eat them right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:43.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Shouldn't we put our things away first?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:46.07,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Eating the year's first souvenir \Ntakes priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:49.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Eating really is all you ever do, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:50.02,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.72,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and eat these!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:54.95,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:35.14,Next Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,6000)}The Place We Longed to Reach
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:29.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I came to Hitotose Manor because \NI wanted to change myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:33.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and I met precious friends there \Nwho can never be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.52,0:23:36.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep working toward my goal \Nalong with all the people I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:39.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "The Place We Longed to Reach."
